{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-15235/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-15235"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["1:52:35"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["eye-level"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["handheld, pan"]}}],"summary":{"none":["Woman's hand grabs book off the shelf"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15235/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-15235","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15235/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-15235"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15235/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15235/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15235/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15235/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15235/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15235/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15235/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15235/canvas/1/fabdfcb5-2ae3-429f-ba2d-ab0cba878b53","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T17:42:09.808Z","creator":"Ada ","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Once again, the way Alma handles the mushroom book, as well the ingredients themselves, mirrors Reynolds’s handling of fabrics.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15235/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:362.357206937799,384.70693779904303,402.1067583732058,517.3923444976076"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15235/canvas/1/d256ca23-9807-4858-8433-959db7cdaf54","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T17:42:26.875Z","creator":"Ada ","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Another book on the shelf, <em>The Observer’s Guide to Dogs</em>, continues the canine minor theme of <em>Phantom Thread</em>. Although Reynolds’s <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW202802351 BCX4\" href=\"https://digbmc.github.io/pt-annotated/items/phan-01942.html\"><u>own dogs</u></a> haven’t been seen since the beginning of the film, the presence of this book reminds audiences of their existence and the dog costume that caused the disruption at the New Year’s Eve party. Dogs, then, are associated with intrusions and, here at least, with the drastic steps Alma takes in her relationship with Reynolds. The other two books seen atop the <em>Guide to Dogs</em> are also from the Observer’s series.</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15235/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:28.77990430622006,758.7828947368421,465.4620215311005,179.48190789473688"}}}]}]}]}